      <title>莱茵金属首席执行官以不断增长的订单放眼全球舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rheinmetall-ceo-eyes-global-stage-with-growing-order-book-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国防务集团莱茵金属公司首席执行官阿明·帕珀格 (Armin Papperger) 周四晚间表示，随着公司的不断发展，公司希望成为一家全球性企业，预计到今年年底积压订单将达到约 600 亿欧元（640 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rheinmetall-ceo-eyes-global-stage-with-growing-order-book-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 08:04:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
